name: AC_CLEANDRIVE
description: Obtained if the player completes 5 laps without getting any damage to the car. Any mode.

name: AC_HOTLAPPER
description: Obtained if the player completes 10 valid laps in Hotlap mode.

name: AC_PRACTICE_10
description: Obtained if the player completes 10 valid laps in Practice mode

name: AC_TIMEATTACK_3
description: Obtained if the player completes 3 laps in Time Attack Mode

name: AC_TIMEATTACK_5
description: Obtained if the player completes 5 laps in Time Attack Mode.

name: AC_TIMEATTACK_10
description: Obtained if the player completes 10 laps in Time Attack Mode.

name: AC_NOASSISTS_PRACTICE
description: Obtained if the player completes 10 laps in practice mode with no assists. If the car has some assist by default, the player must turn them off.

name: AC_DISTANCE_100
description: Obtained if the player drive more than 100 Km in one session

name: AC_DISTANCE_250
description: Obtained if the player drive more than 250 Km in one session

name: AC_COMBO_10
description: Obtained if the player achieves 10 combos in drift mode

name: AC_COMBO_25
description: Obtained if the player achieves 25 combos in drift mode

name: AC_COMBO_50
description: Obtained if the player achieves 50 combos in drift mode

name: AC_DISTANCE_50
description: Obtained if the player drive more than 50 Km in one session
